# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Planned]
|Feature|Example Features|Benefit
|:-|:-|:-|
|Dynamic Filtering|Custom scripts, regex, metadata rules|Extensible, powerful filtering
|Multi-Source|Multiple source dirs, exclusion rules|Manage files from anywhere
|Regrouping|Nested, virtual, tag-based|Dynamic, rule-based file views
|Safety|Conflict handling, dry run, backups|Safe, predictable operation
|Automation|Watch mode, schedules, triggers|Set-and-forget automation
|Cloud/Remote|Cloud storage, remote sync|Extend beyond local storage
|UI/Accessibility|TUI, web dashboard, accessibility|User-friendly, inclusive
|Logging/Reports|Detailed logs, reports, visualization|Transparency, insights
|Collaboration|Shared configs, team workspaces|Community, teamwork
|Performance|Parallel, batch, resume|Scalable, efficient

## [Unreleased]

### Added

- This CHANGELOG file to hopefully keep a track of all features that will be added.
- README to explain the project and how to use it.
- MIT license because we <3 open-source projects.
- List all files extensions in a folder and subfolders



